TRANSPARENCY DASHBOARD ENHANCEMENTS (New):

1. MODULARITY:
   ├─ src/data/mockMetrics.js (static data)
   ├─ src/utils/metrics.js (helper functions)
   ├─ src/components/MetricCard.jsx
   ├─ src/components/AxiomStatus.jsx
   ├─ src/components/FeedbackChart.jsx
   └─ src/components/Footer.jsx

2. TYPE SAFETY (TypeScript):
   interface Metrics {
     gCSI: number;
     nTSV: number;
     cosymbioseStabilitat: number;
     avi: { index: number; status: string };
     nsr: Axiom;
     olf: Axiom;
     tfk: Axiom;
     // ... complete interface
   }

3. REAL-TIME DATA:
   Replace setInterval with Firestore onSnapshot:
   
   const unsubscribe = onSnapshot(
     collection(db, 'metrics'),
     (snap) => {
       const data = snap.docs[0]?.data();
       if (data) setMetrics(data);
     }
   );

4. ACCESSIBILITY:
   ├─ ARIA labels on all icons
   ├─ Semantic HTML (<section>, <header>, <footer>)
   ├─ WCAG AA color contrast verified
   └─ Screen reader compatible

5. PROFESSIONAL CHARTING:
   Replace Tailwind bars with Recharts:
   
   <BarChart data={feedbackData} layout="vertical">
     <XAxis type="number" hide />
     <Bar dataKey="count" fill="#6366F1" />
     <Tooltip />
   </BarChart>

6. SECURITY:
   ├─ .env for sensitive URLs
   ├─ process.env.REACT_APP_FIREBASE_API_KEY
   ├─ process.env.REACT_APP_S3_BUCKET
   └─ No hardcoded credentials

7. LINTING:
   ├─ ESLint with Airbnb/Standard config
   ├─ Prettier for formatting
   └─ react-hooks/exhaustive-deps enabled

